Class QuizSession

    • model.QuizSession

  • public class QuizSession
extends java.lang.Object
    QuizSession.java
    Author:
    swabhat This class encapsulates the data that help keep track of scores in each subject. it contains the following member variables
    • topic name
    • number of questions answered correctly
    • number of questions answered incorrectly
    • total number of questions asked
